{"tid":2074154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微信30萬資金突然被凍結　用戶求助官方：騰訊擁有所有權","createTime":"2020-06-22T01:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T05:52:42.000Z","uid":135867,"like":604,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":129,"replies":[{"pid":"67acb9dcfc6c3c28715d7c97fd85e969f11a3ea6","tid":2074154,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:42:33.000Z","msg":"近日根據國內媒體報導，福州一位經營廣告公司的王女士，平常生活大多時都會利用微信進行交易。近日因她的賬戶涉嫌違規交易，被限制部分收款功能，隨​更​後直接將其賬戶中近30萬資金凍結。<br />\n<a href=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=f7278c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg</a><br />\n圖片來源：<a href=\"http://amazonaws.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazonaws.com&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ca98b9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazonaws.com</a><br />\n<br />\n王女士得知帳戶被凍結後，即時聯繫騰訊客服，並提供企業信息、訂單信息、身份信息等資料，但申訴十多次得到的回座仍是&quot;維持原判&quot;，甚至她都不知道自己犯下哪條所謂的違規交易。<br />\n其後王女士只好向媒體求助，在記者的協助下再次跟騰訊聯絡，竟然得到的回覆居然是「用戶對微信只有使用權，而騰訊卻擁有所有權」<br />\n<a href=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e6a9678b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg</a><br />\n圖片來源：<a href=\"http://amazonaws.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazonaws.com&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ca98b9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazonaws.com</a><br />\n最後在記者介入的第二天，王女士的帳戶就被解封，騰訊方面表示道歉，指今次事件是他們內部出錯，而今次事件曝光後，微信官方在微博上宣傳「請記好：你的錢就是你的錢！」但內地網民對今次事件相當不滿，因為騰訊是沒有權利凍結用戶的資金。<br />\n如果喜歡我們的文章，請即分享到︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=fpimgs%2Es3%2Dap%2Dsoutheast%2D1%2Eamazonaws%2Ecom%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02%2E90466298%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dfpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dfpimgs%252Es3%252Dap%252Dsoutheast%252D1%252Eamazonaws%252Ecom%252Fuul%252F202006%252F200621%252F5eef4203a17e02%252E90466298%252Ejpg&h=8e39800a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bca786e97752ac585185daf65f7f48be14ca77da","tid":2074154,"uid":130693,"like":415,"dislike":1,"score":414,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 今次割錯韮菜<br />\n下次會割唔出聲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04e5fdca12960e34976ecb024801c9c3c4cf7c1","tid":2074154,"uid":335434,"like":186,"dislike":0,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:44:25.000Z","msg":"尋釁滋事  邊個同你講喺共產黨政權下係有私有產權架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221cbe57bff208c7c892894f615e4551bb6b096b","tid":2074154,"uid":173179,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"Your money <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOur money <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704ad10e0a6d1397393e102a28b742fd96aa965d","tid":2074154,"uid":253016,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:45:55.000Z","msg":"筆錢只係支共借比你用"},{"pid":"797bd1eed9c348a173c377cc21c1c727fb9724ee","tid":2074154,"uid":35