20-06-22T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"700 做埋銀行個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ab12437d1cbe0b155a8e0dc76cca6e57741080","tid":2074154,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67acb9dcfc6c3c28715d7c97fd85e969f11a3ea6","tid":2074154,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:42:33.000Z","msg":"近日根據國內媒體報導，福州一位經營廣告公司的王女士，平常生活大多時都會利用微信進行交易。近日因她的賬戶涉嫌違規交易，被限制部分收款功能，隨​更​後直接將其賬戶中近30萬資金凍結。<br />\n<a href=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=f7278c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg</a><br />\n圖片來源：<a href=\"http://amazonaws.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazonaws.com&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ca98b9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazonaws.com</a><br />\n<br />\n王女士得知帳戶被凍結後，即時聯繫騰訊客服，並提供企業信息、訂單信息、身份信息等資料，但申訴十多次得到的回座仍是&quot;維持原判&quot;，甚至她都不知道自己犯下哪條所謂的違規交易。<br />\n其後王女士只好向媒體求助，在記者的協助下再次跟騰訊聯絡，竟然得到的回覆居然是「用戶對微信只有使用權，而騰訊卻擁有所有權」<br />\n<a href=\"https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e6a9678b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg</a><br />\n圖片來源：<a href=\"http://amazonaws.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazonaws.com&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ca98b9d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazonaws.com</a><br />\n最後在記者介入的第二天，王女士的帳戶就被解封，騰訊方面表示道歉，指今次事件是他們內部出錯，而今次事件曝光後，微信官方在微博上宣傳「請記好：你的錢就是你的錢！」但內地網民對今次事件相當不滿，因為騰訊是沒有權利凍結用戶的資金。<br />\n如果喜歡我們的文章，請即分享到︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=fpimgs%2Es3%2Dap%2Dsoutheast%2D1%2Eamazonaws%2Ecom%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02%2E90466298%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dfpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dfpimgs%252Es3%252Dap%252Dsoutheast%252D1%252Eamazonaws%252Ecom%252Fuul%252F202006%252F200621%252F5eef4203a17e02%252E90466298%252Ejpg&h=8e39800a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:26.000Z","msg":"好安全好温暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6823da260958356eda2c2f4bef0321866ad89633","tid":2074154,"uid":15703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"做戲姐<br />\n100個得呢個係假既 其餘99個真係凍結左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb9bf23c40ce0734945698ec9d91ddf699d1f6e","tid":2074154,"uid":149607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cd1c1a43ea3e8866e37c815a1b0d061e7f903fc2","tid":2074154,"uid":68689,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pqbgf8x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqbgf8x.png&h=e3693fae&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"😦😦😦"},{"pid":"d53eda7974ccaf7f5f44c3778291180a169a0bf6","tid":2074154,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:39